results.name: Number of five-dimensional simplical toric diagrams with hypervolume n.
comment: Also gives the number of distinct abelian orbifolds of C^6/Gamma, Gamma in SU(6).
link: J. Davey, A. Hanany and R. K. Seong, Counting Orbifolds, J. High Energ. Phys. (2010) 2010: 10; arXiv:1002.3609 [hep-th], 2010.
A. Hanany and R. K. Seong, Symmetries of abelian orbifolds, J. High Energ. Phys. (2011) 2011: 27; arXiv:1009.3017 [hep-th], 2010-2011.
Andrey Zabolotskiy, Coweight lattice A^*_n and lattice simplices, arXiv:2003.10251 [math.CO], 2020.
